channel.description:
[code]Item.java:449: class, interface, or enum expected item = 15333 Armadyl_Godsword A_beautiful,_heavy_sword. 0 0 0 600 700 900 300 0 600 700 900 300 0 1000 8 ^ 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Thats the error I got. What do I have to do? If you're help works I'll give you rep ++
